    public class ConsoleDebugLogPublisher
extends DebugLogPublisher<DebugLogPublisherCfg>

        Parameters:
        config - The publisher configuration that contains the information to use to initialize this publisher.
        Throws:
        ConfigException - If an unrecoverable problem arises in the process of performing the initialization as a result of the server configuration.
        InitializationException - If a problem occurs during initialization that is not related to the server configuration.
